---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Who We Serve — Plenum AI Systems"
  description="Plenum AI Systems builds AI growth infrastructure for home service businesses: HVAC, plumbing, roofing, electrical, landscaping, pest control, and more."
  ogTitle="Who We Serve — Plenum AI Systems"
  ogDescription="AI systems built for home service businesses that run on booked appointments and customer trust."
  canonical="https://plenumaisystems.com/who-we-serve"
>
  <Nav />

  <!-- Page Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="label">Who We Serve</div>
      <h1>Built for home service businesses.</h1>
      <p>Different businesses, same problem. Leads that go cold. We fix it for every home service vertical that runs on booked appointments and customer trust.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HVAC -->
  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="feature-grid">
        <div>
          <div class="label">HVAC</div>
          <h2>Every missed call is a job you'll never know about.</h2>
          <p>Homeowners don't wait around when their AC breaks in July. They call the next company. Our AI receptionist and missed-call text-back answer in seconds, while reactivation quietly mines the leads who never scheduled that tune-up.</p>
          <p style="margin-top:12px;">Speed is the whole game in HVAC. Our systems respond to every inquiry within 60 seconds — day, night, weekends, and holidays.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card" style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;min-height:280px;">
          <div style="text-align:center;">
            <div style="font-size:3rem;margin-bottom:12px;">❄️</div>
            <h3>HVAC / Heating & Cooling</h3>
            <p style="font-size:0.85rem;margin-top:8px;"><strong>Tune-ups · Repairs · Installations · Maintenance contracts</strong></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Plumbing -->
  <section class="alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="feature-grid">
        <div class="card" style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;min-height:280px;">
          <div style="text-align:center;">
            <div style="font-size:3rem;margin-bottom:12px;">�</div>
            <h3>Plumbing</h3>
            <p style="font-size:0.85rem;margin-top:8px;"><strong>Emergency repairs · Drain cleaning · Water heaters · Installations</strong></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="label">Plumbing</div>
          <h2>Emergency calls can't wait until Monday.</h2>
          <p>When a pipe bursts at 10pm, the homeowner isn't filling out a form and waiting until business hours. They're calling. If nobody answers, they're calling the next plumber. Our AI captures those after-hours calls and starts the conversation immediately.</p>
          <p style="margin-top:12px;">Database reactivation also works exceptionally well for plumbing — past customers who had a repair done 2 years ago and are due for maintenance.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Roofing -->
  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="feature-grid">
        <div>
          <div class="label">Roofing</div>
          <h2>Storm damage doesn't schedule appointments.</h2>
          <p>After a big storm, roofing companies get flooded with inquiries. Most can't keep up. Leads go cold in hours, not days. Our AI handles the initial response, qualifies the urgency, and books inspections — so your crew can focus on the roof, not the phone.</p>
          <p style="margin-top:12px;">Review generation is critical for roofing. One 5-star Google review from a happy homeowner is worth more than any ad spend.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card" style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;min-height:280px;">
          <div style="text-align:center;">
            <div style="font-size:3rem;margin-bottom:12px;">🏠</div>
            <h3>Roofing</h3>
            <p style="font-size:0.85rem;margin-top:8px;"><strong>Repairs · Replacements · Inspections · Storm damage</strong></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Electrical -->
  <section class="alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="feature-grid">
        <div class="card" style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;min-height:280px;">
          <div style="text-align:center;">
            <div style="font-size:3rem;margin-bottom:12px;">�</div>
            <h3>Electrical</h3>
            <p style="font-size:0.85rem;margin-top:8px;"><strong>Repairs · Panel upgrades · Installations · Safety inspections</strong></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="label">Electrical</div>
          <h2>Homeowners research before they call. Be there when they do.</h2>
          <p>Electrical work requires trust. Homeowners check reviews, compare quotes, and take their time deciding. Our review generation and referral engine builds the trust wall that settles the decision in your favor.</p>
          <p style="margin-top:12px;">Lead nurturing keeps you top-of-mind during that consideration window — answering questions, providing estimates, and staying present without being pushy.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Landscaping -->
  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="feature-grid">
        <div>
          <div class="label">Landscaping</div>
          <h2>Seasonal demand spikes. Be ready when homeowners start calling.</h2>
          <p>Landscaping has intense seasonal spikes — spring cleanups, summer maintenance, fall leaf removal, winter snow. When demand hits, you need to capture every lead. Our AI scales with your call volume so nothing falls through the cracks.</p>
          <p style="margin-top:12px;">Database reactivation is gold for landscaping — last year's customers who never rebooked are a goldmine of recurring revenue.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card" style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;min-height:280px;">
          <div style="text-align:center;">
            <div style="font-size:3rem;margin-bottom:12px;">�</div>
            <h3>Landscaping</h3>
            <p style="font-size:0.85rem;margin-top:8px;"><strong>Lawn care · Hardscaping · Tree services · Snow removal</strong></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pest Control -->
  <section class="alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="feature-grid">
        <div class="card" style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;min-height:280px;">
          <div style="text-align:center;">
            <div style="font-size:3rem;margin-bottom:12px;">�</div>
            <h3>Pest Control</h3>
            <p style="font-size:0.85rem;margin-top:8px;"><strong>Inspections · Treatments · Prevention · Emergency removal</strong></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="label">Pest Control</div>
          <h2>Nobody wants to wait when there's a bug problem.</h2>
          <p>Pest control is urgent by nature. When someone sees termites or rodents, they want help now. Our AI receptionist captures those urgent calls instantly, qualifies the issue, and books the appointment — often before a human would have picked up.</p>
          <p style="margin-top:12px;">Recurring service plans are where the real revenue is. Our reactivation campaigns bring back lapsed customers and keep retention high.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Don't see your business? -->
  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <div style="max-width:760px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center;">
        <div class="label">Don't See Your Business?</div>
        <h2>If it's a home service, we've probably thought about it.</h2>
        <p style="margin:22px auto 0;max-width:640px;font-size:1.05rem;">
          The mechanics are the same across home service businesses. Leads that go cold, calls that go unanswered, customers who drift off. If you run a home service business and any of that sounds familiar, the systems work the same for you.
        </p>
        <div style="margin-top:32px;">
<a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">→ Book a Free Audit</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Cold leads, meet warm system.</h2>
      <p>Your next customer may already be in your database, calling your office, or clicking your ad. Plenum AI Systems makes sure they don't disappear.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">→ Book a Free Audit</a>
      <a href="/services" class="btn btn-blue">See Our Services</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
